<h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
    Your privacy is important to us. This page explains how the Privacy Coach application
    handles user data and ensures safe usage.
</p>

<h3>What We Do Not Collect</h3>
<ul>
    <li>We do NOT store your quiz answers permanently.</li>
    <li>We do NOT share your information with any third parties.</li>
    <li>We do NOT track your activity outside the application.</li>
</ul>

<h3>What the Application Uses</h3>
<ul>
    <li>A temporary quiz score stored via TempData (cleared after one use).</li>
    <li>Basic authentication (email/password) if you register an account.</li>
    <li>No external analytics or cookies beyond default .NET Identity.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Your Rights</h3>
<p>
    You may delete your account at any time and no personal information is kept afterward.
</p>

